description: Returns a list of all revisions for the specified configuration.

parameters.name: ConfigurationId
parameters.description: The unique ID that Amazon MQ generates for the configuration.

nested_items.name: ConfigurationId
nested_items.description: The unique ID that Amazon MQ generates for the configuration.

nested_items.name: MaxResults
nested_items.description: The maximum number of configuration revisions that can be returned per page (20 by default). This value must be an integer from 5 to 100.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token that specifies the next page of results Amazon MQ should return. To request the first page, leave nextToken empty.

nested_items.name: Revisions
nested_items.description: The list of all revisions for the specified configuration.

nested_items.name: Created
nested_items.description: Required. The date and time of the configuration revision.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The description of the configuration revision.

nested_items.name: Revision
nested_items.description: Required. The revision number of the configuration.
